name: INSetTaskAttributeTemporalEventTriggerUnsupportedReason
desc: Reasons the app can't modify the temporal event trigger of the task.

items.name: case invalidRecurrence
items.desc: The temporal event trigger refers to an invalid or unsupported schedule for repeating a task.

items.name: case timeInPast
items.desc: The temporal event trigger refers to a moment or time span that has already occurred.
